{"tid":1754541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IT戰線︰更改藍絲長老手機Google搜尋器設定同Follow Facebook專頁！","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T10:40:23.000Z","uid":297148,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"340b525d94ed53bd7aafad080abdb928d33b3ef9","tid":1754541,"uid":297148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"因為我成日幫長老整電腦，整手機Setting，所以我手上有數名藍絲長老嘅Google Account登入資料，仲有長老因為見我部手機拎咗去整，借咗佢部login咗Google Account同Facebook Account嘅舊手機畀我，於是我就唔客氣啦。<br />\n1) 去Facebook follow立場、主場、蘋果、雷霆881、港台、頭條新聞、有線、新聞刺針、眾新聞、沈旭暉、李怡、潘小濤、吳志森、練乙錚、呂秉權、畢明、林超英、莊偉忠、陶傑、王迪詩、陳雲海、伍家謙，我冇follow太黃嘅報紙同人，主要follow佢哋都認識嘅名人同新聞機構，費事引起懷疑。<br />\n2) 設定自製 Google 搜尋引擎排除紅媒搜尋結果<br />\n去呢度睇點做︰<br />\n讓搜尋結果排除你不想看到的網站﹍自製 Google 搜尋引擎教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wfublog.com/2017/02/google-custom-search-engine-exclude-website.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wfublog.com%2F2017%2F02%2Fgoogle-custom-search-engine-exclude-website.html&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=cd4baadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wfublog.com/2017/02/google-custom-search-engine-exclude-website.html</a><br />\n「Google 自訂搜尋」官網：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.google.com/cse/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fcse%2F&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=5cfca6b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.google.com/cse/</a><br />\n排除名單︰<br />\n香港01 &mdash; <a href=\"http://www.hk01.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=b34e8811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hk01.com</a><br />\n東方日報 &mdash; <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=d1423c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc</a><br />\n星島日報 &mdash; <a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=10a80078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com&h=32e48fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">std.stheadline.com</a><br />\n文匯報 &mdash; <a href=\"http://www.wenweipo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenweipo.com&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=bc747037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.wenweipo.com</a><br />\n大公報 &mdash; <a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=684eff2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.takungpao.com.hk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4Hnh43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4Hnh43.png&h=0acda057&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nBy體能垃圾到爆嘅鍵盤戰士"},{"pid":"096a6def30a0d9491418c2c1da85b4cd8e57f635","tid":1754541,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=b6dd5ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQ